==Notes==
<div class="references-small">
{{fnb|1}}During the [[2003-04 NHL season|2003-04 season]], there was a tie between [[Jarome Iginla]] of the [[Calgary Flames]], [[Ilya Kovalchuk]] of the [[Atlanta Thrashers]] and [[Rick Nash]] of the [[Columbus Blue Jackets]].<br />
{{fnb|2}}During the [[1918-19 NHL season|1918-19 season]], there was a tie between [[Newsy Lalonde]] and [[Odie Cleghorn]] of the [[Montreal Canadiens]].<br />
{{fnb|3}}During the [[1935-36 NHL season|1935-36 season]], there was a tie between [[Bill Thoms]] and [[Charlie Conacher]] of the [[Toronto Maple Leafs]].<br />
{{fnb|4}}During the [[1936-37 NHL season|1936-37 season]], there was a tie between [[Larry Aurie]] of the [[Detroit Red Wings]] and [[Nels Stewart]] of the [[New York Americans]].<br />
{{fnb|5}}During the [[1954-55 NHL season|1954-55 season]], there was a tie between [[Maurice Richard]] and [[Bernard Geoffrion]] of the [[Montreal Canadiens]].<br />
{{fnb|6}}During the [[1959-60 NHL season|1959-60 season]], there was a tie between [[Bronco Horvath]] of the [[Boston Bruins]] and [[Bobby Hull]] of the [[Chicago Black Hawks]].<br />
{{fnb|7}}During the [[1979-80 NHL season|1979-80 season]], there was a tie between [[Blaine Stoughton]] of the [[Hartford Whalers]], [[Charlie Simmer]] of the [[Los Angeles Kings]] and [[Danny Gare]] of the [[Buffalo Sabres]].<br />
{{fnb|8}}During the [[1992-93 NHL season|1992-93 season]], there was a tie between [[Alexander Mogilny]] of the [[Buffalo Sabres]] and [[Teemu Selänne]] of the [[Winnipeg Jets]].<br />
{{fnb|9}}The NHL played only 48 games during the [[1994-95 NHL season|1994-95 season]] due to the [[1994-95 NHL lockout]].<br />
{{fnb|10}}During the [[1997-98 NHL season|1997-98 season]], there was a tie between [[Teemu Selänne]] of the [[Mighty Ducks of Anaheim]] and [[Peter Bondra]] of the [[Washington Capitals]].
</div>

